I"œ<p>Hotel Database Information Retrieval System for use by internal employees.</p>

<p>An <a href="#entity-relationship">Entity Relationship Diagram</a> and a <a href="#relational-diagram">Relational Diagram</a> was generated for this database management system. This project was completed in a team of three for MSCI 346: Database Systems final project.</p>

<p>Link to <a href="https://github.com/catai9/hotel-database-system">Github Code</a>.
Technologies used include SQL, PHP, HTML, CSS, Brackets.</p>

<h2 id="application-functionality">Application Functionality</h2>

<h4 id="1-update-booking">1. <strong><a href="#update-booking">Update Booking</a></strong></h4>
<h4 id="2-hotel-availability">2. <strong><a href="#hotel-availability">Hotel Availability</a></strong></h4>
